{"tid":275750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「求中銀巴打」update左既atm機 不接納貴卡？","createTime":"2017-06-08T09:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T09:53:47.000Z","uid":22558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c6f7ae75c4ac684e3a46c22673e128619b09b2e","tid":275750,"uid":22558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"小弟用開中銀 其實先前已經試過用中銀update左既提款機（每個step識倒數30s)，都話不接納貴卡。<br />\n<br />\n咁果陣我無理到 以為係果部機有問題，岩岩諗住響第二部中銀機再禁錢，點知又話不接納。<br />\n<br />\n不過中銀已經關左，無得去問 要等聽日。<br />\n<br />\n我用其他銀通機係成功拎錢既。即係創興果啲機<br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇中銀巴打都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc0183210c45809d5404e32ad92a7784ab2a9ac","tid":275750,"uid":60733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:38:52.000Z","msg":"你確定個張係中銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2b900622cbda12fa8be4df92f30e062d7e4049","tid":275750,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:38:54.000Z","msg":"擦下張卡晶片位置"},{"pid":"09e7650a34dad2225e938267f11776527da8b9a5","tid":275750,"uid":22558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3680d6c33109f72448918705da482c9cc91c339","tid":275750,"uid":22558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你確定個張係中銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用左幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1b0f51734831383f7d357a78824b21f589cced","tid":275750,"uid":22558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擦下張卡晶片位置</blockquote><br />\n應該唔關事？ 岩岩試埋東亞機 一樣用到<img src